<!DOCTYPE html>
<head>
    <title>대용량 파일 다운로드</title>
</head>
<body>
    <style>
        .download-block {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: flex-start;
            align-items: center;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 10px;
            margin: 60px 20px;
        }
        #download {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #18272f;
            font-weight: 700;
            position: relative;
        }
        #download::before {
            content: "";
            background-color: hsla(196, 61%, 58%, 0.75);
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            bottom: -3px;
            width: 100%;
            height: 8px;
            z-index: -1;
            transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;
        }

        #download:hover::before {
            bottom: 0;
            height: 100%;
        }
    </style>
    <script>
        window.onload = function () {
            document.getElementById("download").setAttribute("href", "<%=fileUrl%>");
        };
    </script>
    <div class="download-block">
        <div>아래 문서명을 클릭하면 다운로드가 진행됩니다.</div>
        <a id="download" href=""><%=fileName%></a>
    </div>
</body>
